==English==

====Alternative spellings====
*[[table spoon]]

===Etymology===
[[table]] + [[spoon]]

===Noun===
'''tablespoon''' ([[tablespoons]])

# (''US'') A large spoon, used for eating food from a [[bowl]].
# (''Australia'') A spoon too large for eating, usually used for cooking.
# A unit of measure, equal to three [[teaspoon]]s or roughly 15 [[milliliter]]s.

====Synonyms====
*[[dessertspoon]], [[dessert spoon]] (1, ''Australia'')

